{"tid":293532,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"九巴上客後開車突「反軚」　九巴車長扭傷手","createTime":"2017-06-22T09:02:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-22T12:32:33.000Z","uid":1762,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ad6da744fa2f686a54bc1a0869d874d6278b82aa","tid":293532,"uid":1762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T09:02:40.000Z","msg":"黃大仙發生交通意外。上午11時49分，一輛91M線九巴於龍蟠街3號星河明居對開巴士站上落客後，姓黃（50餘歲）車長遂扭軚開車，期間疑因<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">軚盤太重</span></strong>往反方向轉，致黃左手扭傷，幸巴士未有撞及任何車輛，亦無乘客受傷。警方正調查意外原因<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170622/bkn-20170622125845902-0622_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170622%2Fbkn-20170622125845902-0622_00822_001.html&d=QdXelFQ4I9jJvmzBiBI9wjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=91d87c74\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170622/bkn-20170622125845902-0622_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"a958de3434f23dd052fd3330423b190383dee8fb","tid":293532,"uid":57962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T09:04:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a8e7c29f30b936c215155a9a2760167640ef5360","tid":293532,"uid":5399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T09:09:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i2.kknews.cc/large/c100008c325da77430e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2Flarge%2Fc100008c325da77430e&h=a14a6ed3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n粉軚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d1f908eff455b312ad45caa6bc8d01172b67cb4","tid":293532,"uid":60258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T09:22:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8bdeca7dedbeb8e64a544c206ed037450138768","tid":293532,"uid":7